
============== Conditional ==================
if condition:
  do this
else:
  do this
  
  
============== Neste if /else ==================
if condition:
  if another condition:
    do this
  else:
    do this
else:
  do this
  
  
  ======== if /elif /else ==============
if condition1:
  do A
elif condition2:
  do B
else:
  do this


============== Multiple if  ==================
# all conditionals it will be executed
if condition1: 
  do A
if condition2:
  do B
if condition3:
  do C
